{
  "stem": "8916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He-- he had good friends he worked with.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they received us and put us up for a few days, you know, in their home and everything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Poland was not a very hospitable place to be for Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So inhospitable that people who survived the concentration camps and returned to Poland were actually murdered after the war by the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to funerals of such a thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had been killed by the-- by the Polish nationals after they had survived the-- the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quite a few, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father went back and got-- actually got his job back, the pre-war job, and was going to find out if it's possible to resettle and reestablish his position.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But soon we-- you know, we soon found out that this was not going to be possible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my sister, Aviva, and David went to Czechoslovakia, and we thought maybe we would resettle there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they went sort of as our Leyson scouts to see how this would work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the meantime, the situation in Poland was not-- getting worse, and so we decided to escape from Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So in 1946-- we got back to Poland in 1945-- in 1946, we went-- escaped from Poland and went back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Originally, we thought we would-- since my brother and sister were in Czechoslovakia, that we, on the way to Germany, would get off and join them, but that was not possible.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we ended up in Germany--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in a displaced persons camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Wetzlar.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wetzlar is a city near-- near Giessen and near Frankfurt, Frankfurt am Main.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We remained there for three years.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
